32:04.000Z","msg":"老鼠是游泳高手呢！<br />\n<br />\n家棲鼠類可以通過抽水馬桶潛入高層建築物內。同時老鼠也是游泳高手，它們以後腳划水，以前腳操控方向，尾巴也充當某種方向舵。它們的耐力驚人，能連續踩水3天，而且潛水功夫一流，能在水下閉氣3分鐘。城市四通八達的下水管道，就是老鼠們活動的廣闊舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5aa22dde19a3fe5fb59e52902695a5720dbea8","tid":2099500,"uid":162783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"a plague tale : innocence"},{"pid":"34e214614598ee828f68056831372a660e1f7f04","tid":2099500,"uid":185426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:33:47.000Z","msg":"啲抖音聲真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c099b6d8446ce7f1e134f325a98983fe18389159","tid":2099500,"uid":301092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"華春瑩[我提醒你 中國有14億人]<br />\n<br />\n一人食一隻 老鼠要絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人最愛食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa3c1cfaa081df884d5290be34d3b1fd4ec16ef","tid":2099500,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:34:09.000Z","msg":"冇事，大陸天選之人點會有事"},{"pid":"bce2f667e9a362223cd357f5b32b8c2be7dd3e1b","tid":2099500,"uid":243455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:36:11.000Z","msg":"水浸晒d坑渠 下水道  地下水管，d老鼠咪上晒地面另覓新居 符合蟈蜻"},{"pid":"4fa7806f3a46f21aa6b09686a67d2a49df3c0181","tid":2099500,"uid":300139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:39: